title: Luna's Mama Kitchen
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Western, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Near ALBA and facing L'Architecte, this restaurant is frequented by students and local office employees. Features a recycled and environmental design. Aims to offer fresh and healthy meals with vegan choices in salads, veggie burger, melanzane Sandwich, and a pasta Siciliana - be sure to specify.
